  "prompt": "What ERP software has B2B & B2C eCommerce WebStore Integration?",
  "response": "Several ERP (Enterprise Resource Planning) software systems offer B2B (Business-to-Business) and B2C (Business-to-Consumer) eCommerce webstore integration. Some of the popular ones include:\n\n1. **SAP ERP**:\n   - Offers comprehensive integration with eCommerce platforms for both B2B and B2C operations. SAP Commerce Cloud is a notable solution that integrates seamlessly with SAP ERP.\n\n2. **Microsoft Dynamics 365**:\n   - Integrates well with various eCommerce platforms and provides solutions for both B2B and B2C eCommerce. Dynamics 365 Commerce is a tailored solution for this purpose.\n\n3. **Oracle ERP Cloud**:\n   - Provides robust integration options with eCommerce platforms, facilitating both B2B and B2C transactions. Oracle Commerce Cloud can be integrated with its ERP solutions.\n\n4. **NetSuite**:\n   - Specifically designed to cater to both B2B and B2C eCommerce needs, NetSuite provides SuiteCommerce, which integrates smoothly with its ERP system.\n\n5. **Odoo**:\n   - Offers comprehensive eCommerce modules along with its ERP solution, suitable for managing both B2B and B2C webstores.\n\n6. **Infor CloudSuite**:\n   - Provides integrated solutions for managing B2B and B2C eCommerce, aligning seamlessly with its ERP offerings.\n\n7. **Acumatica**:\n   - Delivers strong eCommerce integration capabilities for both B2B and B2C, offering Acumatica Commerce Edition.\n\n8. **Epicor ERP**:\n   - Facilitates B2B and B2C eCommerce through its various integration options, supporting a seamless connection between eCommerce platforms and ERP functionality.\n\n9. **SYSPRO**:\n   - Provides ERP solutions with integrations for eCommerce operations catering to both B2B and B2C markets.\n\nEach of these ERP systems offers unique features and customization options, so the choice would depend on the specific requirements of your business, including factors like scalability, industry-specific needs, ease of integration, and budget.",
